Setting Repo
＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊

    mkdir ~/bin
    export PATH=~/bin:$PATH
    curl https://raw.github.com/franco-c/Repo/master/repo > ~/bin/repo
    chmod a+x ~/bin/repo

Syncing the Mirage Source
＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊

    mkdir ~/slim
    cd ~/slim
    repo init -u git://github.com/Open-Wise/platform_manifest_slim.git -b jb4.2
    repo sync -f -j12

